  "body": "**üßê Motivation**\n<!-- Is your feature request related to a specific problem? Is it just a crazy idea? Tell us about it! -->not so crazy idea \n\n**üìù Details**\n<!-- Please describe your feature request in detail. --> is that possible to make **unchangeable price for erc20 token** . Example **1Xtoken= USD1 always** . Because this token will only use in spesific environment (ex:VerseX). In this verseX we can play games earn token, trade NFT, buy and sell product, etc. all environment only use Xtoken. So i think no need to change the price based on token activity, no inflation, no dropping price, no up price, no need to compare with up and down USD,etc. because this Xtoken have own currency. Fixed price for 1 token always. Maybe can add voting for democracy.\n\n<!-- Make sure that you have reviewed the OpenZeppelin Contracts Contributor Guidelines. -->\n<!-- https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md -->",
